WEBVTT

42:34.120 --> 42:35.240 line:80%
Manager, bad news!

42:35.350 --> 42:37.600 line:80%
Police runners have forced their way in
through the back door.

42:37.600 --> 42:38.600 line:80%
I'll go there now.

42:39.120 --> 42:39.870 line:80%
I'll go take a look too.

42:39.870 --> 42:40.910 line:80%
I want to know who exactly they are

42:40.910 --> 42:42.840 line:80%
and what they're trying to do here.
